      <hedline>
        <hl1>An Inconvenient Woman</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Chelsea Elisabeth Goodwin letter praises David France's May 28 article on transsexual Calpernia Sarah Addams and murder of Pfc Barry Winchell0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>This was the most sensitive article on transgender issues that I have seen in a mainstream publication. You have illustrated the complexities of gender and sexuality and the ways in which transsexuals get used and abused by assimilationist gay politicians.</p>
        <p>Chelsea Elisabeth Goodwin</p>
        <p>Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
